… I remember how painful it was to just watch Chi-chan as she tried her best to fix the broken train car. [l][r]
...But you know, Chi-chan was really amazing at that time. [l][r]
Sad, sad, sad. Even though I was shaking and crying and screaming, I took a bath, drank some beer, took a break... and then started walking again. [l][r]

[r]……I get it, Chi-chan. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
