That's not the case now. You don't have to aim high, and you don't have to be prepared to walk far with a heavy load. [l][r]
When I go outside my apartment, there is a convenience store right there. I can get anything delivered with just a few taps on my smartphone. [l][r]
[r]... I don't think there's anything good or bad about that. If that's the kind of world we live in, then that's fine. [l][r]
[r]That's what I think, but I can't say anything right now. [l][r]
I don't want to deny what Chi-chan says. I definitely don't want to say that she's wrong. [l][r]
I want to grant you all the things you want. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Because if I don't watch over Chi-chan, she'll be alone again... [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

