Whenever I wake up, he'll be by my side, smiling. [l][r]
He shows me all sorts of things that I might be able to eat and lets me try them. [l][r]
[r]When are you buying it? Are you okay with the money?[r]
Or what happened to school? [l][r]

[r]... I'm worried about it, but I can't bring myself to put it into words.
[_tb_end_text]

