You are kind. [l][r]
You are warm. [l][r]
The yu is soft. [l][r]
You feel comfortable. [l][r]
Yu. Yuu. Yuri... [l][r]
I want to savor that feeling over and over again. Yuri... who is mine alone. [l][r]
